#: ../../agent_skills.rst:2
msgid "Agent Skills（智能体技能）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:5
msgid "概述"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:7
msgid ""
"Agent Skills 是 PersonAgent 的能力插件系统。PersonAgent 本身是轻量编排器， 真正的认知与行为能力由独立 "
"skill 提供（如 observation、memory、cognition、plan）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:10
msgid "当前实现采用两条核心原则："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:12
msgid "**Metadata-first**：选择阶段只暴露 ``name`` + ``description``，不加载完整正文。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Tool-loop**：每步由模型在工具循环里 ``activate_skill`` / ``read_skill`` / "
"``execute_skill``，无固定 pipeline 层级。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:15
msgid "这意味着：技能是否执行由当前上下文与模型选择决定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:19
msgid "设计目标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:21
msgid "**按需加载**：降低每步不必要的加载与执行开销。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:22
msgid "**可解释选择**：选择依据来自 catalog 中的简短描述，便于调试与治理。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:23
msgid "**热更新友好**：支持运行时扫描、导入、启用/禁用与重载。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:24
msgid "**依赖在文档中说明**：需要其它 skill 时在 SKILL.md 正文写明，由模型按需激活。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:28
msgid "Skill 目录结构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:30
msgid "内置技能位于包内目录，自定义技能位于工作区目录："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:51
msgid "Skill 的两种模式（与当前 PersonAgent skills-first 设计一致）："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:53
msgid ""
"**Prompt-only（推荐）**：不声明 ``script``。当模型选择并 activate skill 后，SKILL.md "
"作为行为指南注入上下文，模型使用内置原子工具（bash/codegen/workspace_* 等）完成任务。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Subprocess script（确定性计算/解析用）**：在 frontmatter 中声明 ``script: "
"scripts/my_skill.py``。执行时以子进程运行脚本，参数通过 ``--args-json`` 传入，产物写入 agent "
"workspace（``AGENT_WORK_DIR``）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:58
msgid "SKILL.md 格式"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:60
msgid "每个 skill 目录应包含 ``SKILL.md``。文件头部使用 YAML frontmatter 描述元数据："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:72
msgid "字段说明："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:78
msgid "字段"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:79
msgid "说明"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:80
msgid "``name``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:81
msgid "Skill 名称（唯一标识）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:82
msgid "``description``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:83
msgid "给选择器看的功能描述，尽量具体、可判别。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:85
msgid ""
"可选：包内技能可通过约定 ``scripts/<name>.py`` 提供子进程脚本；框架不在 frontmatter 中解析 "
"``priority`` / ``requires`` / ``inputs`` / ``outputs`` 等扩展字段。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:89
msgid "每步执行流程"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:91
msgid "PersonAgent.step() 的流程如下："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:93
msgid "注入技能 catalog（仅 ``name`` + ``description``）+ 工作区状态 + 最近工具历史。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:94
msgid "进入 tool-loop：模型每轮选择一个工具调用（activate/read/execute/workspace_* 等）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:95
msgid "当调用某个 skill 时，运行时会按需加载完整 SKILL.md 与 skill 目录下的文件。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:96
msgid "达到 done 或轮次上限后结束本 step，并持久化最小会话状态与工具历史。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:98
msgid "关键点："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:100
msgid "**技能** 由能力目录、行为规范与可选子进程脚本组成，而不是框架内固定顺序的 pipeline。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:101
msgid "**渐进披露**：先暴露 catalog，激活后再注入全文，用于减少上下文负担。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:105
msgid "Memory 语义"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:107
msgid "认知相关技能通常先把内容写入 ``_cognition_memory`` 缓冲："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:109
msgid "当 ``memory`` 技能在本步被选中执行时，缓冲会被 flush 到长期记忆。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:110
msgid "当 ``memory`` 未被选中时，缓冲不会丢失，会保留到后续 step。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:111
msgid "在 Agent ``close()`` 时，会执行兜底 flush，避免遗留缓冲丢失。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:113
msgid "因此，memory 行为不再是固定“Finalize 层”，而是由选择结果驱动。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:117
msgid "运行时管理 API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:119
msgid "后端提供 Agent Skills 管理接口（前缀 ``/api/v1/agent-skills``）："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:121
msgid "``GET /list``：列出技能（builtin + custom）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:122
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``POST /scan``：扫描 ``{workspace}/custom/skills``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:123
msgid "``POST /import``：从外部目录导入技能"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:124
msgid "``POST /reload``：热重载单个技能"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:125
msgid "``POST /remove``：删除自定义技能"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:126
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``GET /{name}/info``：查看技能详细信息（含 SKILL.md 内容）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:128
msgid "这些接口同时被 VS Code 扩展与手动调试流程使用。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:132
msgid "自定义 Skill 最小示例"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:134
msgid "目录："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:143
msgid "``SKILL.md``："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:152
msgid "``scripts/hello_skill.py``："
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:173
msgid "导入并启用后，主 LLM 会在合适上下文中选择它执行。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:177
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:179
msgid "``description`` 写成”触发条件 + 输出结果”，便于选择器判断。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:180
msgid "若依赖其它 skill，在正文写清并引导先 ``activate_skill``。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:181
msgid "Skill 代码尽量幂等，避免重复执行造成状态污染。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:182
msgid "对关键技能保留清晰日志，便于复盘每步选择与执行。"
msgstr ""

